Pre-requisites
--------------
My submissions were developed from the Planet Wars' Java Starter Kit
therefore you need at least:
- Java 5+ SDK
- Ant

How to run a game of Planet Wars?
---------------------------------
- just call 'ant' in the root directory
- the game engine will calculate up to 200 turns,
  then the game player will animate each turn till the game is won.

How to change the bots?
-----------------------
- edit build.xml
- set property 'player2' to one of the precompiled bots under lib/example_bots/
- edit src/MyBot.java
- on line 18, instantiate the class of the desired strategy
